      and its entropy extremum is equipartition / vertex concentration
      (R3_Agent2 + EntropyExtremum) — chaining R5_Agent8 ∘ R5_Agent1.

  Depends on (exact lemma names used):
    - MIP.Discoveries.R5_Agent8_MixtureFanoCoverage :
        R5_Agent8_MixtureFanoCoverage.mixture_fano_floor,
        R5_Agent8_MixtureFanoCoverage.mixture_fano_floor_pos,
